        <qualifiedname>mqtt_sn_transport::poll</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Check if incoming data is available. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>If <ref refid="structmqtt__sn__transport_1abe102ec52b34f767d0b231e93bedd0a9" kindref="member">poll()</ref> returns a positive number, recv must not block.</para>
<para>May be NULL, but recv should not block then either.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>Positive number if data is available, or zero if there is none. Negative values signal errors. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
