    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure to describe an MQTT-SN transport. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>MQTT-SN does not require transports to be reliable or to hold a connection. Transports just need to be frame-based, so you can use UDP, ZigBee, or even a simple UART, given some kind of framing protocol is used. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
